putDestinationsOnNetwork

public void putDestinationsOnNetwork(GvFlag[] flags)
                              throws GraphException
We have this method separated from calculate to speed up odmatrix calculations. The developer can position flags once, and call calculate only changing source (idStart). This way, destination flags are positionned only once.
